# User Guide for 2048 AI
By Jianpu Ma jm4437

###Introduction
This is the python program for Columbia University Artificial Intelligent class, simnlating the 2048 gaming process between the Computer and AI, we implement a strategy for our AI to automatically play the game with computer and see the final result.

###Runing guide
To run the program, simply type $ python GameManager.py, and the whole process will be displayed in the terminal screen.


###Algorithm overview
The 2048 game use the iterative deepening search and mini-max pruning algorithm and heuristic function in evaluating the possible move

###Game Performance
We run the program 20 times by the command line
The program has a possibility of reach the 2048 40% of the time.
The best score has reached 4096,the improvement on the game could be integrated with other heuristic function and balanced each weight.









